trans-unit.target: 一維陣列，是從 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> 物件複製之項目的目的端。

trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零起始的索引，會從這個位置開始複製。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> 方法複製整個集合至一維陣列，從目標陣列中所指定的索引開始。

The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.

trans-unit.target: 如果找到的話，則為指定之 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 物件的索引值，否則為 -1。
